locations.name: Daytona Tamworth
locations.description: The Midland's premier kart circuit. Daytona Tamworth is a 1000+ metre multi layout outdoor tarmac circuit just five minutes from the M42 (J10). With Bambino, Junior and Senior karts for private and public events.
